### GET PENDING DOCTORS
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### GET ALL DOCTORS
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### GET SINGLE DOCTOR
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### APPROVE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### REJECT
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

